data.description: Welcome to this Great Home in Fountain of the Sun, A Gated Active Adult Community in East Mesa, 3 BEDROOM 2 bath (1462 sq ft) , 2 Car Garage, Large Open Floor Plan, UPDATED Kitchen w/ Custom Cabinets, Corian Counters and Lots of Storage, Large Living Room, Formal Dining Room,  Primary Bedroom w/ Walk-in Closet, 2 - Guest Bedrooms, Updated Bathroom Vanities,  Washer & Dryer Included, NEW ROOF (2020), Large Lot w/ Beautiful Rosemary Bush & Orange Trees (Valencia, Navel Orange & AZ Sweet), Enjoy the Spectacular AZ Sunsets from your Back Covered Patio Area. Do Not Miss this One!!
